<h1>About Link.ly</h1>

<p>Link.ly aims to provide users with a way to keep all of their favorite websites in an easy-to-access web-app.</p>
<p>There are a huge variety of different browsers, on different platforms, and the typical internet user may use Firefox, Chrome, Safari, or Internet Explorer on a desktop, phone, or tablet and bookmark websites on each one. When it's time to find that one page with that great photo of a cat with a top hat you really want to show your friends, it takes forever to remember where you saved it! What a hassle!</p>

